    .container
      / ROUNDED IMAGES
      / Images marked as responsive have a max-width equal to the screen. You can add rounded corners with img-rounded, img-circle, and img-thumbnail. pull-left and pull-right will float images in the provided direction. center-block will place the image in the center.
      %img#nttLogo.img-responsive.img-thumbnail.pull-left{:alt => "Responsive image", :src => "ntt-logo.png"}/
      / CONTEXTUAL COLORS
      / Contextual colors can be added to text
      %p
        %span.text-muted Quis nostrud
        %span.text-primary exercitation ullamco
        %span.text-success laboris nisi
        %span.text-info ut aliquip
        %span.text-warning ex ea commodo
        %span.text-danger consequat.
        Duis aute irure dolor in reprehenderit in voluptate velit esse cillum dolore eu fugiat nulla pariatur.
